      "patchset_number": 10,
      "line": 64,
      "message": "VES OpenApi Manager uses SDC Distribution Client as library/dependency. SDC Client requires us to pass SDC BE HTTPS url for its initialization.\n\nFrom this application point of view, it's only for configuration of this client. I don't really know how SDC client uses it underneath, but somehow it works.",
